<div class="panel">
	<h3><i class="icon icon-tags"></i> {l s='Documentation' mod='addtocartshaker'}</h3>
	<p>
		&raquo; {l s='This module allows your static product pages become more engaging by animating the add to cart button driving your visitors focus toward taking action.
The animation creates urgency and an impulse to complete a purchase. Your potential customers will feel compelled to click the \'add to cart\' button raising your site\'s conversion rate instantly.' mod='addtocartshaker'}
	</p>
	<p>
		&raquo; {l s='Ensure your "Add to Cart" button has the ".add-to-cart" class or the module will not work' mod='addtocartshaker'} :
	</p>
</div>

<div class="panel">
	<h3><i class="icon icon-desktop"></i> {l s='Demo' mod='addtocartshaker'}</h3>
	<p>
		{l s='This is a demo with the animation type and visual settings selected' mod='addtocartshaker'}
	</p>
	<br><br>

	<div class="add">
		<button class="btn btn-primary add-to-cart" >
			<i class="material-icons shopping-cart">&#xE547;</i>
			{l s='Add to cart' d='Shop.Theme.Actions'}
		</button>
	</div>
	<br><br>
	<p>
		{l s='This animation will only execute 3 times to don\'t disturb users' mod='addtocartshaker'}
	</p>

</div>
